      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Pekaûs / Remalijus defenitâ Gaddâ Jotama Usiju winna Leel-Kunga Dehls / dar- Dehla.\nrïja weenu Derribu prett winnu /\nun kawe to eekfch Samarijas\nceksch ta Kehnixa Namina Pa-\ngalmja/ ar Argobu un ar Arju/\nun ar winnu bija peezeefmits\nWihrn no Gileada Behrneem/\nun nokawe to/ un tas tappe par\nKehnizu winna Weetâ."
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kas wehl no Peka-\nus Leetahm atleek/ un wifs/ ko\nwiꞥſch irr darrïjs/ raugi/ tas irr\nrakstihts to Israëta Kehnizu\nLaiku-Grahmata."
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Peektâdefiniti ohtrâ Gad-\ndâ Asarijus ta Kehnixa no Juh-\nda/ tappe Pekaûs Remalijus\nDehls par Kehnizu par Israëlu\neekfch Samarijas/ ( un waldir-\nja) diwidefmits Gaddus."
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch darrïja / kas\ntam KUNGAM ne patieke/\nwiꞥſch ne afstahjehs no Jerobea-\nma Neebata Dehla Grehkeem/\nkas Israëlu grehkoht darrïjs."
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pekaûfa ta Israëta\nKehnixa Laikâ atnahze Tiglat\nPillefers tas Kehniſsch no Af-\nfirtjas/ un ussehnue Jöuu/ un\nAbel Bet-Meakn/ un Janon/ un\nRedes/ un Azoru/ nn Gileadu /\nun Galileju/ un wiffu Nawtata\nSemmi/ un nowedde tohs ue\nAffirijn."
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Ofeus Ella Dehls dar-\nrïja weenu Derribu prett Peka-\nusfu Remalijus Dehlu/ un kawe\nto/ un nokawe to/ un tappe par\nKehnizu winna Weetâ/ dtwi-"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kas wehl no Pekaï\nLeetahm atleek/ un wifs/\nwiꞥſch irr darrïjs/ raugi/ tas\nrakstihts to Israëta Kehni-\nLaiku-Grahmata."
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ohtrâ Gaddâ Pekaï\nRemalijus Dehla ta Israë\nKehnixa / tappe Jotams Usij\nDehls par Kehnizu pahr Juhd"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Diwidefmits peezeus Ga\ndus wezz bija wiꞥſch/ kad win-\npar Kehnizu tappe/ un waldf\nfechpadefmits Gaddus Jeru\nlemê / un winna Mahteï b\nJerusa Wahrdn/ Zadaka Mei"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch darrïja /\ntam KUNGAM labbi patif\npehz wiffu/ ko winna Teh\nUsijus bij darrïjs."
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tee Augstnimi ween\ntappe nopohstiti/ tee Laudis\npureja un kwehpinaja wehl\nteim Augstumeem. Schis\ntaffija tahs augstas Wahrtis\nta KUNGA Namna."
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kas wehl no Jota\nLeetahm atleek / un wifs/\nwiꞥſch irr darrïjs / tas irr\nsthts to Kehnizu no Juhda\nku - Grahmata."
    },
    {
      "n": 37,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tanni Laikâ fahze\nKUNGS eekfch Juhda fuh\nRezinn to Sihrezu Kehnizu/\nPekaûfu Remalijus Dehlu."
    },
    {
      "n": 38,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Jotams aismitgg\nfaveein Tehweein/ un tappe\nfaveein Tehweem aprakts D\nwida fava Tehwa Pilli."
    }
  ],
